    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car price tag, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
