    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a true 'time capsule' specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom scent; the premium leather bolsters remain firm and uncreased, while the dashboard and trim are free of any fading or imperfections. Every switch, button, and electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is indistinguishable from new, supported by a comprehensive binder of every service record since its delivery. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, having never been exposed to inclement weather. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
